#: index.docbook:2872 index.docbook:2878 index.docbook:2884 index.docbook:2890
#: index.docbook:2896
#, no-c-format
msgid "embedded.pluginmap"
msgstr "embedded.pluginmap"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides a wide range of options for plots. Most plotting plugins utilize "
"this."
msgstr ""
"Zagotavlja široko paleto možnosti za grafikone. Večina vtičnikov za risanje "
"uporablja to."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2849
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plots->Barplot, most other plotting plugins"
msgstr "Plots->Barplot, večina drugih vtičnikov za risanje"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2852
#, no-c-format
msgid "rkward::color_chooser"
msgstr "rkward::color_chooser"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2854
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Very simple plugin for specifying a color. Current implementation provides a "
"list of color names. Future implementations may provide more elaborate color "
"picking."
msgstr ""
"Zelo preprost vtičnik za določanje barve. Trenutna izvedba ponuja seznam "
"imen barv. Prihodnje izvedbe lahko zagotovijo bolj dovršeno izbiranje barv."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2856 index.docbook:2868
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plots->Histogram"
msgstr "Grafi->Histogram"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2859
#, no-c-format
msgid "rkward::plot_stepfun_options"
msgstr "rkward::plot_stepfun_options"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2861
#, no-c-format
msgid "Step function plot options"
msgstr "Možnosti izrisa stopenjske funkcije"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2862
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plots->ECDF plot"
msgstr "Parcele->risba ECDF"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2865
#, no-c-format
msgid "rkward::histogram_options"
msgstr "rkward::histogram_options"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2867
#, no-c-format
msgid "Histogram (plot) options"
msgstr "Možnosti histograma (risbe)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2871
#, no-c-format
msgid "rkward::barplot_embed"
msgstr "rkward::barplot_embed"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2873
#, no-c-format
msgid "Barplot options"
msgstr "Možnosti stolpičnega grafa"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2874 index.docbook:2880 index.docbook:2886
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plots->Barplot"
msgstr "Grafikoni->Stolpični grafikon"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2877
#, no-c-format
msgid "rkward::one_var_tabulation"
msgstr "rkward::one_var_tabulation"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2879
#, no-c-format
msgid "Provides tabulation on a single variable."
msgstr "Zagotavlja tabeliranje ene same spremenljivke."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2883
#, no-c-format
msgid "rkward::limit_vector_length"
msgstr "rkward::limit_vector_length"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2885
#, no-c-format
msgid "Limit the length of a vector (to the n largest or smallest elements)."
msgstr "Omejite dolžino vektorja (na n največjih ali najmanjših elementov)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2889
#, no-c-format
msgid "rkward::level_select"
msgstr "rkward::level_select"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provides a &lt;valueselector&gt; filled with the levels (or unique values) "
"of a vector."
msgstr ""
"Zagotavlja &lt;valueselector&gt; napolnjen z ravnmi (ali edinstvenimi "
"vrednostmi) vektorja."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2892 index.docbook:2898
#, no-c-format
msgid "Data->Recode Categorical data"
msgstr "Podatki->Prekodiraj kategorične podatke"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2895
#, no-c-format
msgid "rkward::multi_input"
msgstr "rkward::multi_input"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:2897
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Combines spinbox, input and radio controls to provide input for character, "
"numeric, logical data."
msgstr ""
"Združuje vrtilno polje, vnosne in radijske kontrole za zagotavljanje vnosa "
"znakovnih, številskih in logičnih podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2905
#, no-c-format
msgid "Elements for use in &pluginmap; files"
msgstr "Elementi za uporabo v datotekah &pluginmap;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2909
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Needs to be present in each &pluginmap; file as the root-node (exactly "
"once). Attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Prisoten mora biti v vsaki datoteki &pluginmap; kot korensko vozlišče "
"(natanko enkrat). Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2912
#, no-c-format
msgid "base_prefix"
msgstr "base_prefix"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2913
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Filenames specified in the &pluginmap; file are assumed to be relative to "
"the directory of the &pluginmap; file + the prefix you specify here. Useful, "
"esp., if all your components are located below a single subdirectory."
msgstr ""
"Imena datotek, navedena v datoteki &pluginmap;, so pričakovano relativne "
"glede na imenik datoteke &pluginmap; + predpono, ki jo navedete tukaj. "
"Uporabno, zlasti če se vse vaše komponente nahajajo pod enim samim "
"podimenikom."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2916
#, no-c-format
msgid "namespace"
msgstr "namespace"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2917
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A namespace for the component ids. When looking up components for embedding, "
"the components will be retrievable via a string \"namespace::component_id\". "
"Set to \"rkward\" for now."
msgstr ""
"Imenski prostor za ID-je komponent. Ko iščete komponente za vdelavo, jih bo "
"mogoče pridobiti prek niza \"namespace::component_id\". Zaenkrat nastavite "
"na \"rkward\"."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2920 index.docbook:3068 index.docbook:3092 index.docbook:3114
#: index.docbook:3146 index.docbook:3164 index.docbook:3210 index.docbook:3232
#: index.docbook:3246 index.docbook:3278
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>id</term>"
msgstr "<term>id</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2921
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An optional identifier string for this &pluginmap;. Specifying this allows "
"third authors to refer to and load your &pluginmap; from theirs (see <link "
"linkend=\"chapter_dependencies\">chapter on handling dependencies</link>)."
msgstr ""
"Izbirni identifikatorski niz za ta &pluginmap;. Če navedete to možnost, "
"lahko tretji avtorji sklicujejo in naložijo vašo datoteko &pluginmap; od "
"njihovih (glejte <link linkend=\"chapter_dependencies\">poglavje o ravnanju "
"z odvisnostmi</link>)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2924
#, no-c-format
msgid "priority"
msgstr "priority"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2925
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One of <replaceable>\"hidden\"</replaceable>, <replaceable>\"low\"</"
"replaceable>, <replaceable>\"medium\"</replaceable>, or <replaceable>\"high"
"\"</replaceable>. &pluginmap;s with priority \"medium\" or \"high\" are "
"activated, automatically, when &rkward; first finds them. Use "
"<replaceable>priority=\"hidden\"</replaceable> for &pluginmap;s that are not "
"meant to be activated, directory (only meant for inclusion). In the current "
"implementation this does not actually hide the &pluginmap;, however. "
"(Optional, defaults to \"medium\")."
msgstr ""
"En od <replaceable>\"hidden\"</replaceable>, <replaceable>\"low\"</"
"replaceable>, <replaceable>\"medium\"</replaceable> ali <replaceable>\"high"
"\"</replaceable>. &pluginmap; s prioriteto \"medium\" ali \"high\" se "
"aktivirajo samodejno, ko jih &rkward; prvič najde. Uporabite "
"<replaceable>priority=\"hidden\"</replaceable> za &pluginmap;, ki niso "
"namenjeni za aktiviranje, imenik (namenjen samo za vključitev). V trenutni "
"izvedbi pa to dejansko ne skrije &pluginmap;. (Izbirno, privzeto je \"medium"
"\")."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2930
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;dependencies&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;dependencies&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2931
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This element, specifying dependencies, is allowed as a direct child of the "
"&lt;document&gt; element (once), and as a child of &lt;component&gt; "
"elements (once for each &lt;component&gt; element). Specifies the "
"dependencies that must be met in order to use the plugin(s). See the <link "
"linkend=\"chapter_dependencies\">chapter on dependencies</link> for an "
"overview. Attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Ta element, ki določa odvisnosti, je dovoljen kot neposredni podrejeni "
"element elementa &lt;document&gt; (enkrat) in kot podrejeni element &lt;"
"component&gt; elementov (enkrat za vsak element &lt;component&gt;). Podaja "
"odvisnosti, ki morajo biti izpolnjene za uporabo vtičnika(-ov). Za pregled "
"glejte <link linkend=\"chapter_dependencies\">poglavje o odvisnostih</link>. "
"Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2934
#, no-c-format
msgid "rkward_min_version, rkward_max_version"
msgstr "rkward_min_version, rkward_max_version"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2935
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Minimum and maximum allowed version of &rkward;. Version specifications may "
"include non-numeric suffixes, like \"0.5.7z-devel1\". If a specified "
"dependency is not met, the plugin(s) it applies to <emphasis>will be "
"ignored</emphasis>. <link linkend=\"sect_dependencies_rkward_version\">More "
"information</link>. Optional; if not specified, no minimum / maximum version "
"of &rkward; will be required."
msgstr ""
"Najmanjša in največja dovoljena različica &rkward;. Specifikacije različice "
"lahko vključujejo neštevilske pripone, kot je \"0.5.7z-devel1\". Če določena "
"odvisnost ni izpolnjena, bodo vtičniki, na katere se nanaša, "
"<emphasis>prezrti</emphasis>. <link linkend="
"\"sect_dependencies_rkward_version\">Več informacij</link>. Neobvezno; če ni "
"navedeno, ni najmanjše/največje različice &rkward; bo zahtevano."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2938
#, no-c-format
msgid "R_min_version, R_max_version"
msgstr "R_min_version, R_max_version"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2939
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Minimum and maximum allowed version of &R;. Version specifications may "
"<emphasis>not</emphasis> include non-numeric suffixes, like \"0.5.7z-"
"devel1\". The &R; version dependency will be shown on the plugins' help "
"pages, but does not have any direct effect, as of &rkward; 0.6.1. <link "
"linkend=\"sect_dependencies_r_version\">More information</link>. Optional; "
"if not specified, no minimum / maximum version of &R; will be required."
msgstr ""
"Najmanjša in največja dovoljena različica &R;. Specifikacije različice morda "
"<emphasis>ne</emphasis> vključujejo neštevilske pripone, kot je \"0.5.7z-"
"devel1\". &R; odvisnost od različice bo prikazana na straneh s pomočjo "
"vtičnikov, vendar nima neposrednega učinka, saj od &rkward; 0.6.1. <link "
"linkend=\"sect_dependencies_r_version\">Več informacij</link>. Neobvezno; če "
"ni navedeno, ni najmanjše/največje različice &R; bo obvezno."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2942
#, no-c-format
msgid "platforms"
msgstr "platforme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2943
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Platforms where this plugin is available. Supported values are <replaceable>"
"\"unix\"</replaceable>, <replaceable>\"windows\"</replaceable>, <replaceable>"
"\"macos\"</replaceable>, <replaceable>\"any\"</replaceable>, and colon "
"separated combinations (e.g. <replaceable>\"unix:macos\"</replaceable>). "
"<replaceable>\"unix\"</replaceable> includes any Linux and BSD variants but "
"<emphasis>not</emphasis> MacOS. If your plugin is not platform dependent, "
"just omit this attribute."
msgstr ""
"Platforme, kjer je ta vtičnik na voljo. Podprte vrednosti so <replaceable>"
"\"unix\"</replaceable>, <replaceable>\"windows\"</replaceable>, <replaceable>"
"\"macos\"</replaceable>, <replaceable>\"any\"</replaceable> in kombinacije "
"ločene z dvopičjem (npr. <replaceable>\"unix:macos\"</replaceable>). "
"<replaceable>\"unix\"</replaceable> vključuje vse različice Linuxa in BSD, "
"vendar <emphasis>ne</emphasis> MacOS. Če vaš vtičnik ni odvisen od "
"platforme, preprosto izpustite ta atribut."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2950
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;package&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;package&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2951
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adds a dependency on a specific &R; package. Attributes:"
msgstr "Doda odvisnost od določenega &R; paketa. Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2954 index.docbook:2973 index.docbook:2995
#, no-c-format
msgid "name"
msgstr "name"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2955
#, no-c-format
msgid "Package name (required)."
msgstr "Ime paketa (obvezno)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2958 index.docbook:2977
#, no-c-format
msgid "min_version, max_version"
msgstr "min_version, max_version"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2959 index.docbook:2978
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimum / maximum allowed version (optional)."
msgstr "Najmanjša / največja dovoljena različica (neobvezno)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2962
#, no-c-format
msgid "repository"
msgstr "repository"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2963
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Repository where the package can be found. Optional, but highly recommended, "
"if the package is not available on CRAN."
msgstr ""
"Repozitorij, kjer je paket mogoče najti. Izbirno, vendar zelo priporočljivo, "
"če paket ni na voljo na CRAN."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2969
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;pluginmap&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;pluginmap&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2970
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adds a dependency on a specific &rkward; &pluginmap;. Attributes:"
msgstr "Doda odvisnost od določene &rkward; &pluginmap;. Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2974
#, no-c-format
msgid "Id string of the required &pluginmap; (required)."
msgstr "Id niz zahtevane &pluginmap; (obvezno)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2981 index.docbook:3011 index.docbook:3046
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>url</term>"
msgstr "<term>url</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2982
#, no-c-format
msgid "&URL; where the &pluginmap; can be found. Required."
msgstr "&URL; kjer je &pluginmap; mogoče najti. Obvezno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2992
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"May be present exactly once as a direct child of the &lt;document&gt; "
"element. Contains meta information on the &pluginmap; (or plugin). See the "
"<link linkend=\"chapter_about_information\">chapter on 'about' information</"
"link> for an overview. Attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Lahko je prisoten natanko enkrat kot neposredni podrejeni element elementa "
"&lt;document&gt;. Vsebuje meta informacije o &pluginmap; (ali o vtičniku). "
"Za pregled si oglejte <link linkend=\"chapter_about_information\">poglavje o "
"informacijah 'o'</link>. Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2996
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"User visible name. Optional. Does not have to be the same as the \"id\"."
msgstr "Uporabniku vidno ime. Neobvezno. Ni nujno, da je enak \"id\"."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2999
#, no-c-format
msgid "version"
msgstr "version"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Version number. Optional. The format is not restricted, but to be on the "
"safe side, please follow common versioning schemes such as \"x.y.z\"."
msgstr ""
"Številka različice. Neobvezno. Oblika zapisa ni omejena, vendar zaradi "
"varnosti upoštevajte običajne sheme za ustvarjanje različic, kot je \"x.y.z"
"\"."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3003
#, no-c-format
msgid "releasedate"
msgstr "releasedate"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3004
#, no-c-format
msgid "Release date specification. Optional in format \"YYYY-MM-DD\"."
msgstr "Specifikacija datuma izdaje. Izbirno v obliki \"YYYY-MM-DD\"."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3007
#, no-c-format
msgid "shortinfo"
msgstr "shortinfo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3008
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <emphasis>short</emphasis> description of the plugin / &pluginmap;. "
"Optional."
msgstr "<emphasis>short</emphasis> opis vtičnika / &pluginmap;. Neobvezno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3012
#, no-c-format
msgid "&URL; where more information can be found. Optional, but recommended."
msgstr ""
"&URL; kjer lahko najdete več informacij. Neobvezno, vendar priporočljivo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3015
#, no-c-format
msgid "copyright"
msgstr "copyright"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3016
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copyright specification, &eg; \"2012-2013 by John Doe\". Optional, but "
"recommended."
msgstr ""
"Specifikacija avtorskih pravic, &eg; \"2012-2013 avtor John Doe\". "
"Neobvezno, vendar priporočljivo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3019
#, no-c-format
msgid "licence"
msgstr "licence"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"License specification, &eg; \"GPL\" or \"BSD\". Please make sure to "
"accompany your files with a complete copy of the relevant licence. Optional, "
"but recommended."
msgstr ""
"Specifikacija licence, &eg; \"GPL\" ali \"BSD\". Svojim datotekam ne "
"pozabite priložiti popolne kopije ustrezne licence. Neobvezno, vendar "
"priporočljivo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3023
#, no-c-format
msgid "category"
msgstr "category"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3024
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Category of plugin(s), &eg; \"Item response theory\". As of &rkward; 0.6.1, "
"no categories are predefined. Optional."
msgstr ""
"Kategorija vtičnikov, &eg; \"\"Item response theory\". Od &rkward; 0.6.1, "
"nobena kategorija ni vnaprej določena. Neobvezno."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3030
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;author&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;author&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3031
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adds information on an author. Attributes:"
msgstr "Doda podatke o avtorju. Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3034
#, no-c-format
msgid "name, given, family"
msgstr "ime, ime2, družina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3035
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Either specify the full name for <parameter>name</parameter>, or specify "
"both <parameter>given</parameter> and <parameter>family</parameter>, "
"separately."
msgstr ""
"Bodisi navedite polno ime za <parameter>name</parameter> ali pa navedite "
"tako <parameter>given</parameter> kot <parameter>family</parameter> ločeno."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3038
#, no-c-format
msgid "role"
msgstr "role"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3039
#, no-c-format
msgid "Author role description (optional)."
msgstr "Opis vloge avtorja (neobvezno)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3042
#, no-c-format
msgid "email"
msgstr "email"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3043
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"E-mail address, where author can be contacted. Required. May be set to the "
"rkward-devel mailing list, if you are subscribed, and your plugin is meant "
"to be included in the official &rkward; release."
msgstr ""
"Elektronski naslov, na katerega je avtor dosegljiv. Obvezno. Lahko se "
"nastavi na poštni seznam rkward-devel, če ste naročeni in je vaš vtičnik "
"namenjen vključitvi v uradno izdajo &rkward;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3047
#, no-c-format
msgid "&URL; with more information on the author, &eg; homepage (optional)."
msgstr "&URL; z več podatki o avtorju, &eg; domača stran (neobvezno)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3056
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>&lt;components&gt;</term>"
msgstr "<term>&lt;components&gt;</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Needs to be present exactly once as a direct child of the &lt;document&gt; "
"element. Contains the individual &lt;component&gt;-elements described below. "
"No attributes."
msgstr ""
"Prisoten mora biti natanko enkrat kot neposredni podrejeni element &lt;"
"document&gt; element. Vsebuje posamezne elemente &lt;component&gt;, opisane "
"spodaj. Brez atributov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3060
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;component&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;component&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3061
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One or more &lt;component&gt; elements should be given as direct children of "
"the &lt;components&gt; element (and only there). Registers a component/"
"plugin with rkward. Attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Ena ali več elementov &lt;component&gt; je treba podati kot neposredne "
"podrejene elemente &lt;components&gt; element (in samo tam). Registrira "
"komponento/vtičnik z rkward. Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3064
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>type</term>"
msgstr "<term>type</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3065
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For future extension: The type of component/plugin. Always set to \"standard"
"\" for now (the only type currently supported)."
msgstr ""
"Za prihodnjo razširitev: Vrsta komponente/vtičnika. Zaenkrat vedno "
"nastavljen na \"standard\" (edina trenutno podprta vrsta)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3069
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ID by which this component can be retrieved (for placing it in the menu "
"(see below), or for embedding). See &lt;document&gt;-namespace above."
msgstr ""
"ID, po katerem je mogoče pridobiti to komponento (za postavitev v meni "
"(glejte spodaj) ali za vdelavo). Glejte &lt;document&gt;-namespace zgoraj."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3072 index.docbook:3174
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>file</term>"
msgstr "<term>file</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3073
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Required at least for components of type=\"standard\": The filename of the "
"&XML; file describing the &GUI;."
msgstr ""
"Zahtevano vsaj za komponente type=\"standard\": ime datoteke &XML; datoteka, "
"ki opisuje &GUI;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3076 index.docbook:3118
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>label</term>"
msgstr "<term>label</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3077
#, no-c-format
msgid "The label for this component, when placed in the menu hierarchy."
msgstr "Oznaka za to komponento, ko je postavljena v hierarhijo menija."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3080
#, no-c-format
msgid "optional"
msgstr "neobvezno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3081
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only meaningful for components with defined <link linkend="
"\"chapter_dependencies\">dependencies</link>: Usually, it is considered a "
"reportable error, if a component is not compatible with this version of "
"RKWard. However, if the component really is not needed in the current "
"environment, setting this attribute to <replaceable>\"true\"</replaceable> "
"suppresses any warning (<replaceable>\"false\"</replaceable> by default)."
msgstr ""
"Smiselno samo za komponente z definiranimi <link linkend="
"\"chapter_dependencies\">odvisnostmi</link>: Običajno velja za napako, ki jo "
"je treba prijaviti, če komponenta ni združljiva s to različico RKWard. "
"Vendar, če komponenta v trenutnem okolju res ni potrebna, nastavitev tega "
"atributa na <replaceable>\"true\"</replaceable> privzeto zavrne vsa "
"opozorila (<replaceable>\"false\"</replaceable>)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3088
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;attribute&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;attribute&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3089
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Defines an attribute of a component. Only meaningful for <link linkend="
"\"context_import\">import plugins</link> so far. Only allowed as a direct "
"child of &lt;component&gt;. Attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Določa atribut komponente. Zaenkrat smiselno samo za <link linkend="
"\"context_import\">vtičnike za uvoz</link>. Dovoljeno samo kot neposredni "
"podrejeni &lt;component&gt;. Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3093
#, no-c-format
msgid "Id of the attribute"
msgstr "ID atributa"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3096
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>value</term>"
msgstr "<term>value</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3097
#, no-c-format
msgid "Value of the attribute"
msgstr "Vrednost atributa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Label associated with the attribute"
msgstr "Oznaka, povezana z atributom"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3106
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;hierarchy&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;hierarchy&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Needs to be present exactly once as a direct child of the &lt;document&gt; "
"element. Describes where the components declared above should be placed in "
"the menu hierarchy. Accepts only &lt;menu&gt; elements as direct children. "
"No attributes."
msgstr ""
"Prisoten mora biti natanko enkrat kot neposredni podrejeni element &lt;"
"document&gt;. Opisuje, kje v hierarhiji menija naj bodo postavljene zgoraj "
"navedene komponente. Sprejme samo elemente &lt;menu&gt;  kot neposredno "
"podrejene. Brez atributov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3110
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;menu&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;menu&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One or more &lt;menu&gt; elements should be given as direct children of the "
"&lt;hierarchy&gt; element. Declares a new (sub-)menu. If a menu by the given "
"ID (see below) already exists, the two menus are merged. The &lt;menu&gt; "
"element is allowed either as a direct child of the &lt;hierarchy&gt; element "
"(top level menu), or as the direct child on any other &lt;menu&gt; element "
"(sub-menu). Conversely, the &lt;menu&gt; element accepts other &lt;menu&gt; "
"elements or &lt;entry&gt; elements as children. Attributes:"
msgstr ""
"En ali več elementov &lt;menu&gt; je treba podati kot neposredne potomce "
"elementa &lt;hierarchy&gt;. Razglasi nov (pod)meni. Če meni z danim ID-jem "
"(glejte spodaj) že obstaja, se oba menija združita. Element &lt;menu&gt; je "
"dovoljen kot neposredni podrejeni element &lt;hierarchy&gt; element (meni "
"najvišje ravni) ali kot neposredni podrejeni element katerega koli drugega "
"elementa &lt;menu&gt; (podmeni). Nasprotno pa element &lt;menu&gt; sprejme "
"druge elemente &lt;menu&gt; ali elemente &lt;entry&gt; kot podrejene. "
"Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An identifier string of the menu. Useful, when menu definitions are read "
"from several &pluginmap; files, to make sure plugins can be placed in the "
"same menu(s). Some menu-ids such as \"file\" refer to predefined menus (in "
"this case the \"File\" menu). Be sure to check with existing &pluginmap; "
"files to use consistent ids."
msgstr ""
"Identifikacijski niz menija. Uporabno, ko so definicije menija prebrane iz "
"več datotek &pluginmap;, da zagotovite, da je vtičnike mogoče postaviti v "
"iste menije. Nekateri ID-ji menijev, kot je \"file\", se nanašajo na vnaprej "
"določene menije (v tem primeru meni \"File\"). Ne pozabite preveriti z "
"obstoječo datoteko &pluginmap; za uporabo doslednih ID-jev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3119
#, no-c-format
msgid "A label for the menu."
msgstr "Oznaka za meni."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3122 index.docbook:3136 index.docbook:3154
#, no-c-format
msgid "group"
msgstr "group"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3123 index.docbook:3137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows to control ordering of menu entries. See <link linkend="
"\"pluginmap_grouping\">menu item ordering</link>. Optional."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča nadzor vrstnega reda vnosov v meniju. Glejte <link linkend="
"\"pluginmap_grouping\">razvrstitev elementov menija</link>. Neobvezno."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3128
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;entry&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;entry&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A menu entry, &ie; a menu option to invoke a plugin. May be used only as a "
"direct child of a &lt;menu&gt; element, accepts no child elements. "
"Attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Vnos v meni, &ie; možnost menija za priklic vtičnika. Lahko se uporablja "
"samo kot neposredni podrejeni element &lt;menu&gt; elementa, ne sprejema "
"podrejenih elementov. Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3132
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>component</term>"
msgstr "<term>component</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ID of the component that should be invoked, when this menu entry is "
"activated."
msgstr ""
"ID komponente, ki jo je treba priklicati, ko je aktiviran ta menijski vnos."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3142
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;group&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;group&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Declares a group of items in the menu. See <link linkend=\"pluginmap_grouping"
"\">menu item ordering</link>. Attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Razglasi skupino elementov v meniju. Glejte <link linkend="
"\"pluginmap_grouping\">razvrstitev elementov menija</link>. Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3147
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of this group."
msgstr "Ime te grupe."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3150
#, no-c-format
msgid "separated"
msgstr "separated"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optional. If set to \"true\" the item in this group will be visually "
"separated from surrounding items."
msgstr ""
"Neobvezno. Če je nastavljeno na \"true\", bo element v tej grupi vizualno "
"ločen od okoliških elementov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3155
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the group to append this group to (optional)."
msgstr "Ime grupe, ki ji želite dodati to grupo (neobvezno)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3160
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;context&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;context&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Declares the entries in a <link linkend=\"contextualized_plugins\">context</"
"link>. Only allowed as a direct child of the &lt;document&gt; tag. Accepts "
"only &lt;menu&gt; tags as direct children. Attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Razglasi vnose v <link linkend=\"contextualized_plugins\">context</link>. "
"Dovoljeno samo kot neposredni podrejeni element oznake &lt;document&gt;. "
"Sprejme samo oznake &lt;menu&gt; kot neposredno podrejene. Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ID of the context. Only two contexts are implemented so far: \"x11\" and "
"\"import\"."
msgstr ""
"ID konteksta. Zaenkrat sta implementirana samo dva konteksta: \"x11\" in "
"\"import\"."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3170
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;require&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;require&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Include another &pluginmap; file. This &pluginmap; file is only loaded once, "
"even if it is &lt;require&gt;d from several other files. The most important "
"use case is to include a pluginmap file, which declares some components, "
"which are embedded by components declared in this &pluginmap;. &lt;"
"require&gt;-elements are only allowed as direct children of the &lt;"
"document&gt;-node. Attributes:"
msgstr ""
"Vključi še eno datoteko &pluginmap;. Ta datoteka &pluginmap; se naloži samo "
"enkrat, tudi če je zahtevana - &lt;require&gt;d iz več drugih datotek. "
"Najpomembnejši primer uporabe je vključitev datoteke pluginmap, ki deklarira "
"nekatere komponente, ki so vdelane s komponentami, deklariranimi v tem "
"&pluginmap;. Elementi &lt;require&gt; so dovoljeni samo kot neposredno "
"podrejeni vozlišča &lt;document&gt;. Lastnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The filename of the &pluginmap; to include. This is seen relative to the "
"directory of the current &pluginmap; file + the base_prefix (see above, &lt;"
"document&gt;-element). If you do not know the relative path to the "
"&pluginmap; to be included, use the <parameter>map</parameter> attribute to "
"refer to it by id, instead."
msgstr ""
"Ime datoteke vključeno v &pluginmap;. To je vidno glede na imenik trenutne "
"datoteke &pluginmap; + base_prefix (glejte zgoraj, element &lt;"
"document&gt;). Če ne poznate relativne poti do datoteke &pluginmap; če jo "
"želite vključiti, uporabite atribut <parameter>map</parameter>, da se nanj "
"sklicujete z ID-jem."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3178
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>map</term>"
msgstr "<term>map</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To include a &pluginmap; file from a different package (or an &rkward; "
"&pluginmap; from your external &pluginmap;), you can refer to it by its "
"<replaceable>namespacename::id</replaceable>, as specified in the required "
"&pluginmap;s &lt;document&gt; element. Inclusion will fail, if no "
"&pluginmap; by that id is known (&eg; not installed on the user's system). "
"You should use this method for including &pluginmap;s outside your package, "
"only. For maps inside your package, specifying a relative path "
"(<parameter>file</parameter> attribute) is faster, and more reliable."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vključiti &pluginmap; datoteke iz drugega paketa (ali &rkward; "
"&pluginmap; iz vaše zunanje &pluginmap;), se lahko nanjo sklicujete po "
"njenem <replaceable>namespacename::id</replaceable>, kot je določeno v "
"zahtevanem elementu &pluginmap; &lt;document&gt;. Vključitev ne bo uspela, "
"če &pluginmap; s tem ID-jem ni znan (&eg; ni nameščen v uporabnikovem "
"sistemu). To metodo uporabite samo za vključitev &pluginmap; zunaj vašega "
"paketa. Za mape v vašem paketu je podajanje relativne poti (atribut "
"<parameter>file</parameter>) hitrejše in zanesljivejše."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Elements for use in .rkh (help) files"
msgstr "Elementi za uporabo v datotekah .rkh (pomoč)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Needs to be present in each <literal role=\"extension\">.xml</literal> file "
"as the root-node (exactly once). No attributes."
msgstr ""
"Prisoten mora biti v vsaki datoteki <literal role=\"extension\">.xml</"
"literal> kot korensko vozlišče (natančno enkrat). Brez atributov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3194
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;title&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;title&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Title of the help page. This is <emphasis>not</emphasis> interpreted for "
"help pages for a plugin (this takes the title from the plugin itself), only "
"for stand-alone pages. No attributes. The text contained within the &lt;"
"title&gt; tag will become the caption of the help page. May only be defined "
"once, as a direct child of the &lt;document&gt; node."
msgstr ""
"Naslov strani s pomočjo. To se <emphasis>ne</emphasis> interpretira za "
"strani s pomočjo za vtičnik (to vzame naslov iz samega vtičnika), samo za "
"samostojne strani. Brez atributov. Besedilo v &lt;title&gt; bo postalo "
"naslov strani s pomočjo. Lahko se definira samo enkrat, kot neposredni "
"podrejeni element vozlišča &lt;document&gt;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3198
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;summary&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;summary&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A short summary of the help page (or what this plugin is used for). This "
"will always be shown at the top of the help page. No attributes. The text "
"contained within the &lt;summary&gt; tag will be displayed. Recommended but "
"not required. May only be defined once, as a direct child of the &lt;"
"document&gt; node."
msgstr ""
"Kratek povzetek strani s pomočjo (ali za kaj se ta vtičnik uporablja). To bo "
"vedno prikazano na vrhu strani s pomočjo. Brez atributov. Besedilo v oznaki "
"&lt;summary&gt; bo prikazano. Priporočeno, vendar ni obvezno. Lahko se "
"definira samo enkrat, kot neposredni podrejeni element vozlišča &lt;"
"document&gt;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3202
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;usage&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;usage&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A slightly more elaborate summary of the usage. This will always be shown "
"directly after the &lt;summary&gt;. No attributes. The text contained within "
"the &lt;usage&gt; tag will be displayed. Recommended for plugin help pages, "
"but not required. May only be defined once, as a direct child of the &lt;"
"document&gt; node."
msgstr ""
"Nekoliko bolj podroben povzetek uporabe. To bo vedno prikazano neposredno za "
"&lt;summary&gt;. Brez atributov. Besedilo v oznaki &lt;usage&gt; bo "
"prikazano. Priporočeno za strani s pomočjo vtičnikov, ni pa obvezno. Lahko "
"se definira samo enkrat, kot neposredni podrejeni element vozlišča &lt;"
"document&gt;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3206
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;section&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;section&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A general purposes section. May be used any number of times as a direct "
"child of the &lt;document&gt; node. These sections are displayed in the "
"order of their definition, but all <emphasis>after</emphasis> the &lt;"
"usage&gt; section and <emphasis>before</emphasis> the &lt;settings&gt; "
"section. The text contained within the &lt;section&gt; tag will be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Razdelek za splošne namene. Lahko se uporabi poljubno število krat kot "
"neposredni podrejeni element vozlišča &lt;document&gt;. Ti razdelki so "
"prikazani po vrstnem redu njihove definicije, vendar vsi <emphasis>za</"
"emphasis> &lt;usage&gt; in <emphasis>pred</emphasis> razdelkom &lt;"
"settings&gt;. Besedilo v znaki &lt;section&gt; bo prikazano."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An identifier needed to jump to this section from the navigation bar (or a "
"link). Needs to be unique within the file. Required, no default."
msgstr ""
"Identifikator, potreben za skok na ta razdelek iz navigacijske vrstice (ali "
"povezave). V datoteki mora biti edinstven. Zahtevano, ni privzeto."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3214 index.docbook:3236 index.docbook:3250
#, no-c-format
msgid "title"
msgstr "title"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3215
#, no-c-format
msgid "The title (caption) of this section. Required, no default."
msgstr "Naslov (napis) tega razdelka. Zahtevano, ni privzeto."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3218
#, no-c-format
msgid "short_title"
msgstr "short_title"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A short title suitable to be displayed in the navigation bar. Optional, "
"defaults to the full title."
msgstr ""
"Kratek naslov, primeren za prikaz v navigacijski vrstici. Neobvezno, "
"privzeto je polni naslov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3224
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;settings&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;settings&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Defines the section containing reference on the various &GUI; settings. Only "
"meaningful and only used for plugin related help pages. Use as a direct "
"child of the &lt;document&gt;. May contain only &lt;setting&gt; and &lt;"
"caption&gt; elements as direct children. No attributes."
msgstr ""
"Določa razdelek, ki vsebuje reference na različne nastavitve &GUI;. Samo "
"smiselno in uporabljeno samo za strani s pomočjo, povezane z vtičniki. "
"Uporabi kot neposrednega podrejenega elementa &lt;document&gt;. Lahko "
"vsebuje samo elemente &lt;setting&gt; in &lt;caption&gt; kot neposredne "
"podrejene. Brez atributov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3228
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;setting&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;setting&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Explains a single setting in the &GUI;. Only allowed as a direct child of "
"the &lt;settings&gt; element. The text contained within the element is "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Razlaga posamezno nastavitev v &GUI;. Dovoljeno samo kot neposredni "
"podrejeni element elementa &lt;settings&gt;. Prikaže se besedilo v elementu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ID of the setting in the plugin <literal role=\"extension\">.xml</"
"literal>. Required, no default."
msgstr ""
"ID nastavitve v vtičniku <literal role=\"extension\">.xml</literal>. "
"Zahtevano, ni privzete vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An optional title for the setting. If omitted (omission is recommended in "
"most cases), the title will be taken from the plugin <literal role="
"\"extension\">.xml</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Neobvezni naslov za nastavitev. Če je izpuščen (v večini primerov je "
"priporočljiva izpustitev), bo naslov vzet iz vtičnika <literal role="
"\"extension\">.xml</literal>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3242
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;caption&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;caption&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A caption to visually group several settings. May only be used as a direct "
"child of the &lt;settings&gt; element."
msgstr ""
"Napis za vizualno združevanje več nastavitev. Lahko se uporablja le kot "
"neposredni podrejeni element elementa &lt;settings&gt;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ID of the corresponding element (typically a &lt;frame&gt;, &lt;page&gt; "
"or &lt;tab&gt;) in the plugin <literal role=\"extension\">.xml</literal>."
msgstr ""
"ID ustreznega elementa (običajno &lt;frame&gt;, &lt;page&gt; ali &lt;"
"tab&gt;) v vtičniku <literal role=\"extension\">.xml</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An optional title for the caption. If omitted (omission is recommended in "
"most cases), the title will be taken from the plugin <literal role="
"\"extension\">.xml</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Izbirni naslov za napis. Če je izpuščen (v večini primerov je priporočljiva "
"izpustitev), bo naslov vzet iz vtičnika <literal role=\"extension\">.xml</"
"literal>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3256
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;related&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;related&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Defines a section containing links to further related information. Will "
"always be displayed after the &lt;settings&gt; section. No attributes. The "
"text contained within the &lt;related&gt; tag will be displayed. Typically "
"this will contain an &HTML;-style list. Recommended for plugin help pages, "
"but not required. May only be defined once, as a direct child of the &lt;"
"document&gt; node."
msgstr ""
"Določa razdelek s povezavami do nadaljnjih povezanih informacij. Bo vedno "
"prikazano za razdelkom &lt;settings&gt;. Brez atributov. Besedilo v oznaki "
"&lt;related&gt; bo prikazano. Običajno bo to vsebovalo seznam v slogu "
"&HTML;. Priporočeno za strani s pomočjo vtičnikov, ni pa obvezno. Lahko se "
"definira samo enkrat, kot neposredni podrejeni element vozlišča &lt;"
"document&gt;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3260
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;technical&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;technical&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Defines a section containing technical information of no relevance to end "
"users (such as internal structure of the plugin). Will always be displayed "
"last in a help page. No attributes. The text contained within the &lt;"
"related&gt; tag will be displayed. Not required, and not recommended for "
"most plugin help pages. May only be defined once, as a direct child of the "
"&lt;document&gt; node."
msgstr ""
"Določa razdelek, ki vsebuje tehnične informacije, ki niso pomembne za končne "
"uporabnike (kot je notranja struktura vtičnika). Vedno bo prikazan zadnji na "
"strani s pomočjo. Brez atributov. Besedilo v oznaki &lt;related&gt; bo "
"prikazano. Ni potrebno in ni priporočljivo za večino strani s pomočjo "
"vtičnikov. Lahko se definira samo enkrat, kot neposredni podrejeni element "
"vozlišča &lt;document&gt;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3264
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;link&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;link&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3265
#, no-c-format
msgid "A link. Can be used in any of the sections described above."
msgstr ""
"Povezava. Lahko se uporablja v katerem koli od zgoraj opisanih razdelkov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3268
#, no-c-format
msgid "href"
msgstr "href"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The target &URL;. Note that several &rkward; specific &URL;s are available. "
"See <link linkend=\"pluginhelp\">section on writing help pages</link> for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Ciljni &URL;. Upoštevajte, da je na voljo več specifičnih &URL; za &rkward;. "
"Za podrobnosti si oglejte <link linkend=\"pluginhelp\">razdelek o pisanju "
"strani za pomoč</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3274
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;label&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;label&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts the value of a UI label. Can be used in any of the sections "
"described above."
msgstr ""
"Vstavi vrednost oznake uporabniškega vmesnika. Lahko se uporablja v katerem "
"koli od zgoraj opisanih razdelkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The id of the element in the plugin, of which to copy the "
"<replaceable>label</replaceable>-attribute."
msgstr ""
"ID elementa v vtičniku, za katerega želite kopirati atribut "
"<replaceable>label</replaceable>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3284
#, no-c-format
msgid "&lt;various &HTML; tags&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;various &HTML; tags&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most basic &HTML; tags are allowed within the sections. Please keep manual "
"formatting to a minimum, however."
msgstr ""
"Najbolj osnovne oznake &HTML; so dovoljene v razdelkih. Prosimo, da "
"minimalno uporabljate ročno oblikovanje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Functions available for &GUI; logic scripting"
msgstr "Funkcije, ki so na voljo za &GUI; logično skriptiranje"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Class \"Component\""
msgstr "Razred \"Component\""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Class which represents a single component or component-property. The most "
"important instance of this class is the variable \"gui\" which is predefined "
"as the root property of the current component. The following methods are "
"available for instances of class \"Component\":"
msgstr ""
"Razred, ki predstavlja posamezno komponento ali lastnost komponente. "
"Najpomembnejši pojavek tega razreda je spremenljivka \"gui\", ki je vnaprej "
"določen kot korenska lastnost trenutne komponente. Za pojavke razreda "
"\"Component\" so na voljo naslednje metode:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3295
#, no-c-format
msgid "absoluteId(base_id)"
msgstr "absoluteId(base_id)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the absolute ID of <emphasis>base_id</emphasis>, or - if base_id is "
"omitted - the identifier of the component."
msgstr ""
"Vrne absolutni ID <emphasis>base_id</emphasis> ali – če je base_id izpuščen "
"– identifikator komponente."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3296
#, no-c-format
msgid "getValue(id)"
msgstr "getValue(id)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Discouraged. Use <function>getString(), getBoolean(), or getList()</"
"function>, instead. Returns the value of the given child property. Returns "
"the value of this property, if ID is omitted."
msgstr ""
"Odsvetovano. Namesto tega uporabite <function>getString(), getBoolean() ali "
"getList()</function>. Vrne vrednost dane podrejene lastnosti. Vrne vrednost "
"te lastnosti, če je ID izpuščen."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3297
#, no-c-format
msgid "getString(id)"
msgstr "getString(id)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the value of the given child property as a string. Returns the value "
"of this property, if ID is omitted."
msgstr ""
"Vrne vrednost dane podrejene lastnosti kot niz. Vrne vrednost te lastnosti, "
"če je ID izpuščen."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3298
#, no-c-format
msgid "getBoolean(id)"
msgstr "getBoolean(id)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the value of the given child property as a boolean (if possible). "
"Returns the value of this property, if ID is omitted."
msgstr ""
"Vrne vrednost dane podrejene lastnosti kot boolovo vrednost (če je mogoče). "
"Vrne vrednost te lastnosti, če je ID izpuščen."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3299
#, no-c-format
msgid "getList(id)"
msgstr "getList(id)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the value of the given child property as an array of strings (if "
"possible). Returns the value of this property, if ID is omitted."
msgstr ""
"Vrne vrednost podane podrejene lastnosti kot matriko nizov (če je mogoče). "
"Vrne vrednost te lastnosti, če je ID izpuščen."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3300
#, no-c-format
msgid "setValue(id, value)"
msgstr "setValue(id, value)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the value of the given child property to <emphasis>value</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite vrednost dane podrejene lastnosti na <emphasis>value</emphasis>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3301
#, no-c-format
msgid "getChild(id)"
msgstr "getChild(id)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Return an instance of the child-property with the given <emphasis>id</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr "Vrne pojavek podrejene lastnosti z danim <emphasis>id</emphasis>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3302
#, no-c-format
msgid "addChangeCommand(id, command)"
msgstr "addChangeCommand(id, command)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Execute <replaceable>command</replaceable> whenever the child property given "
"by <emphasis>id</emphasis> changes. <replaceable>id</replaceable> may either "
"be given as a single string, or as an array of ids (if the function is to be "
"called for changes in several properties. <replaceable>command</replaceable> "
"is a callable value (usually a function), however, for compatibility with "
"plugins written for earlier versions of RKWard, it may also be given as a "
"string to be evaluated."
msgstr ""
"Izvedi <replaceable>ukaz</replaceable> vsakič, ko se spremeni podrejena "
"lastnost, ki jo poda <emphasis>id</emphasis>. <replaceable>id</replaceable> "
"je lahko podan kot en sam niz ali kot polje ID-jev (če naj se funkcija "
"pokliče za spremembe več lastnosti). <replaceable>ukaz</replaceable> je "
"klicna vrednost (običajno funkcija), vendar jo je zaradi združljivosti z "
"vtičniki, napisanimi za starejše različice RKWard, mogoče podati tudi kot "
"niz, ki ga je treba ovrednotiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The function returns the parameter <replaceable>command</replaceable>, for "
"convenience (so you can e.g. assign it to a variable and/or call it during "
"initialization)."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija vrne parameter <replaceable>command</replaceable>, zaradi lažje "
"uporabe (da ga lahko npr. dodelite spremenljivki in/ali ga pokličete med "
"inicializacijo)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Class \"RObject\""
msgstr "Razred \"RObject\""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Class which represents a single &R; object. An instance of this class can be "
"obtained by using <command>makeRObject(objectname)</command>. The following "
"methods are available for instances of class \"RObject\":"
msgstr ""
"Razred, ki predstavlja en predmet v &R;. Pojavek tega razreda lahko dobite z "
"uporabo <command>makeRObject(objectname)</command>. Za pojavke razreda "
"\"RObject\" so na voljo naslednje metode:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If any commands are still pending in the backend, the information provided "
"by these methods can be out-of-date by the time that the plugin code is run. "
"Do <emphasis>not</emphasis> rely on it for critical operations (risking loss "
"of data)."
msgstr ""
"Če so kateri koli ukazi še vedno na čakanju v ozadju, so lahko informacije, "
"ki jih zagotovijo te metode, zastarele do trenutka, ko se zažene koda "
"vtičnika. <emphasis>Ne</emphasis> zanašajte se nanj pri kritičnih operacijah "
"(tveganje izgube podatkov)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3309
#, no-c-format
msgid "getName()"
msgstr "getName()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the absolute name of the object."
msgstr "Vrne absolutno ime predmeta."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3310
#, no-c-format
msgid "exists()"
msgstr "exists()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns whether the object exists. You should generally check this before "
"using any of the methods listed below."
msgstr ""
"Vrne, ali predmet obstaja. Na splošno morate to preveriti, preden uporabite "
"katero koli od spodaj navedenih metod."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3311
#, no-c-format
msgid "dimensions()"
msgstr "dimensions()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns an array of dimensions (similar to <command>dim()</command> in R)."
msgstr "Vrne niz dimenzij (podobno kot <command>dim()</command> v R)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3312
#, no-c-format
msgid "classes()"
msgstr "classes()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns an array of classes (similar to <command>class()</command> in R)."
msgstr "Vrne matriko razredov (podobno kot <command>class()</command> v R)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3313
#, no-c-format
msgid "isClass(class)"
msgstr "isClass(class)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns true, if the object is of class <emphasis>class</emphasis>."
msgstr "Vrne true, če je objekt razreda <emphasis>class</emphasis>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3314
#, no-c-format
msgid "isDataFrame()"
msgstr "isDataFrame()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3314
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns true, if the object is a data.frame."
msgstr "Vrne true, če je objekt data.frame."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3315
#, no-c-format
msgid "isMatrix()"
msgstr "isMatrix()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3315
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns true, if the object is a matrix."
msgstr "Vrne true, če je objekt matrix."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3316
#, no-c-format
msgid "isList()"
msgstr "isList()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns true, if the object is a list."
msgstr "Vrne true, če je objekt seznam."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3317
#, no-c-format
msgid "isFunction()"
msgstr "isFunction()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3317
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns true, if the object is a function."
msgstr "Vrne true, če je objekt funkcija."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3318
#, no-c-format
msgid "isEnvironment()"
msgstr "isEnvironment()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns true, if the object is an environment."
msgstr "Vrne true, če je objekt okolje."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3319
#, no-c-format
msgid "isDataNumeric()"
msgstr "isDataNumeric()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3319
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns true, if the object is a vector of numeric data."
msgstr "Vrne true, če je objekt vektor številskih podatkov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3320
#, no-c-format
msgid "isDataFactor()"
msgstr "isDataFactor()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns true, if the object is a vector of factor data."
msgstr "Vrne true, če je objekt vektor faktorskih podatkov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3321
#, no-c-format
msgid "isDataCharacter()"
msgstr "isDataCharacter()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns true, if the object is a vector of character data."
msgstr "Vrne true, če je objekt vektor znakovnih podatkov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3322
#, no-c-format
msgid "isDataLogical()"
msgstr "isDataLogical()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns true, if the object is a vector of logical data."
msgstr "Vrne true, če je objekt vektor logičnih podatkov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3323
#, no-c-format
msgid "parent()"
msgstr "parent()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns an instance of \"RObject\" representing the parent of this object."
msgstr ""
"Vrne pojavek \"RObject\", ki predstavlja nadrejenega elementa tega predmeta."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3324
#, no-c-format
msgid "child(childname)"
msgstr "child(childname)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns an instance of \"RObject\" representing the child "
"<emphasis>childname</emphasis> of this object."
msgstr ""
"Vrne pojavek \"RObject\", ki predstavlja podrejeno <emphasis>childname</"
"emphasis> tega predmeta."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Class \"RObjectArray\""
msgstr "Razred \"RObjectArray\""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An array of RObject instances. An instance of this class can be obtained by "
"using <command>makeRObjectArray(objectnames)</command>. It is particularly "
"useful when dealing with varslots which allow to select multiple objects."
msgstr ""
"Niz primerkov RObject. Primerek tega razreda lahko dobite z uporabo "
"<command>makeRObjectArray(objectnames)</command>. Še posebej je uporabno pri "
"delu z varsloti, ki omogočajo izbiro več predmetov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3330
#, no-c-format
msgid "include()-function"
msgstr "include()-function"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>include(filename)</command> can be used to include a separate JS "
"file."
msgstr ""
"<command>include(ime datoteke)</command> lahko uporabite za vključitev "
"ločene datoteke JS."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3333
#, no-c-format
msgid "doRCommand()-function"
msgstr "doRCommand()-function"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Obsolete. Do not use in new plugins:</emphasis> "
"<command>doRCommand(command, callback)</command>. Use <command>new "
"RCommand()</command>, instead."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Zastarelo. Ne uporabljajte v novih vtičnikih:</emphasis> "
"<command>doRCommand(command, callback)</command>. Namesto tega uporabljajte "
"<command>new RCommand()</command>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:3336
#, no-c-format
msgid "new RCommand()-function"
msgstr "new RCommand()-function"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>new RCommand(command, optional_id)</command> can be used to query "
"&R; for information. Please read the section on <link linkend="
"\"querying_r_for_info\">querying &R; from inside a plugin</link> for "
"details, and caveats."
msgstr ""
"<command>new RCommand(command, optional_id)</command> se lahko uporabi za "
"poizvedbo &R; za informacije. Za podrobnosti in opozorila preberite razdelek "
"o <link linkend=\"querying_r_for_info\">poizvedbi &R; iz vtičnika</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Troubleshooting during plugin development"
msgstr "Odpravljanje težav med razvojem vtičnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"So you have read all the documentation, did everything right, and still "
"cannot get it to work? Do not worry, we will work it out. First thing to do "
"is: Activate <guilabel>&rkward; Debug Messages</guilabel> - window "
"(available from the <guimenu>Windows</guimenu> - menu, or right click on one "
"of the tool bars), and then start your plugin, again. As a general rule of "
"thumb, you should not see any output in the messages window when your plugin "
"gets invoked, or at any other time. If there is one, it is likely related to "
"your plugin. See if it helps you."
msgstr ""
"Torej ste prebrali vso dokumentacijo, naredili vse pravilno, pa še vedno ne "
"morete spraviti v delo? Brez skrbi, uredili bomo. Prva stvar, ki jo morate "
"storiti, je: Aktivirajte <guilabel>&rkward; Sporočila o odpravljanju napak</"
"guilabel> - okno (na voljo v meniju <guimenu>Windows</guimenu> - ali z "
"desnim klikom na eno od orodnih vrstic) in nato znova zaženite svoj vtičnik. "
"Splošno pravilo je, da v oknu s sporočili ne smete videti nobenega izhoda, "
"ko je priklican vaš vtičnik ali kadar koli drugje. Če obstaja, je verjetno "
"povezan z vašim vtičnikom. Poglejte, če vam pomaga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If everything seems fine on the console, try to increase the debug-level "
"(from the command line, using <command>rkward --debug-level 3</command>, or "
"by setting debug level to 3 in <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &rkward;</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Debug</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>). Not all messages shown at higher debug levels "
"necessarily indicate a problem, but chance are, your problem shows up "
"somewhere between the messages."
msgstr ""
"Če se zdi, da je na konzoli vse v redu, poskusite povečati raven "
"odpravljanja napak (v ukazni vrstici z uporabo <command>rkward --debug-level "
"3</command> ali tako, da nastavite raven odpravljanja napak na 3 v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu >Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &rkward;"
"</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Odpravljanje napak</guimenuitem></menuchoice>). "
"Ni nujno, da vsa sporočila, prikazana na višjih ravneh odpravljanja napak, "
"kažejo na težavo, vendar je verjetno, da se vaša težava pojavi nekje med "
"sporočili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you still cannot find out what is wrong, do not despair. We know this is "
"complicated stuff, and - after all - possibly you have also come across a "
"bug in &rkward;, and &rkward; needs to be fixed. Just write to the "
"development mailing list, and tell us about the problem. We will be happy to "
"help you."
msgstr ""
"Če še vedno ne morete ugotoviti, kaj je narobe, ne obupajte. Vemo, da je to "
"zapletena stvar in – navsezadnje – morda ste tudi vi naleteli na napako v "
"&rkward; in &rkward; je treba popraviti. Samo pišite na poštni seznam za "
"razvoj in nam povejte o težavi. Z veseljem vam bomo pomagali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, even if you found out how to do it on your own, but found the "
"documentation to be not-so-helpful or even wrong in some respects, please "
"tell us on the mailing list as well, so we can fix/improve the documentation."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje, tudi če ste izvedeli, kako to storiti sami, vendar ste ugotovili, "
"da dokumentacija ni preveč koristna ali celo napačna v nekaterih pogledih, "
"nam to sporočite tudi na poštnem seznamu, da bomo lahko popravili/izboljšali "
"dokumentacijo."

#. Tag: title
